<h3><a href="http://blog.achotelexperts.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/dean-randazzo-inlet-surf-shop.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-357" title="Dean Randazzo Inlet Surf Shop" src="http://blog.achotelexperts.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/dean-randazzo-inlet-surf-shop-300x199.jpg" alt="Inlet Surf Shop Gardener's Basin Atlantic City" width="300" height="199" /></a><strong>Inlet Surf Shop &#8211; New!</strong></h3>
<p>800 New Hampshire Ave, Atlantic City, NJ 08401</p>
<p>(Gardner&#8217;s Basin) <a title="Inlet Surf Shop Atlantic City, NJ" href="http://www.facebook.com/pages/INLET-SURF/314603001944677">Inlet Surf Shop on Facebook</a></p>
<p>New Jersey&#8217;s most decorated surfer, Dean Randazzo has announced that he will open Inlet Surf Shop at Gardner&#8217;s Basin in Atlantic City in partnership with Tom Forkin on Memorial Day Weekend May 26, 2012.  The shop will be the only &#8220;Surf Shop&#8221; in Atlantic City and will offer all kinds of cool clothing, Dean Randazzo Surfboards, skateboards, sunglasses, wetsuits and much more.</p>
<p>Gardner&#8217;s Basin is a hidden, and lessor known gem in Atlantic City, it has ample free parking, restaurants and bars, the AC Aquarium, fishing charters and fishing bulkhead, boating charters and some really cool shops.</p>
<blockquote><p><strong>Inlet Surf Shop</strong><br />
Gardner&#8217;s Basin<br />
800 N. New Hampshire ave<br />
Atlantic City, NJ 08401</p></blockquote>
<p><strong>Shop Directions:</strong>  From anywhere in Atlantic City, travel north on Atlantic Ave past <a href="http://www.achotelexperts.com/casinos/revel-casino.html" class="kblinker" title="More about Revel Casino &raquo;">Revel Casino</a>, <strong>Turn Left</strong> on N. New Hampshire Ave and travel to the end, Gardner&#8217;s Basin on left with ton&#8217;s of free parking.</p>
<p>Check Out Dean&#8217;s other interests: <a title="Surfboards By DR" href="http://randazzoindustries.com/">Dean Randazzo Surf Boards</a> and <a title="DRCF Cancer Foundation" href="http://www.deanrandazzocancerfoundation.org/">Dean Randazzo Cancer Foundation</a><br />
<iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/qh54uruNI4g" frameborder="0" width="475" height="271"></iframe></p>
]]></content:encoded>
