		<title>New Parking Garage Opens in Atlantic City, NJ</title>
		<link>http://blog.achotelexperts.com/new-parking-garage-opens-in-atlantic-city-nj/</link>
		<comments>http://blog.achotelexperts.com/new-parking-garage-opens-in-atlantic-city-nj/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 21 Mar 2012 15:48:16 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Atlantic City Guy</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Atlantic City, NJ]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[atlantic city parking garage]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[new atlantic city parking]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[parking facility atlantic city]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://blog.achotelexperts.com/?p=335</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[Atlantic City, New Jersey &#8211; An amazing new parking facility has opened in Atlantic City at Fairmount ave and Mississippi ave at the Atlantic City Expressway.  The garage is in place to create easy access parking for patrons for Tanger Outlets, the Walk, as well as convention center overflow and parking for larger events in Atlantic City like the Airshow or events at Boardwalk Hall.  Basically the garage supports the entire Atlantic City Tourism District. When I say this is a state-of-the-art parking facility, it may be an understatement.  The cost to build was $32 million, features such as 1,677 solar panels on the top floor that generate over 400 kilowatt hours per day, glass enclosed elevators, over 16,000 square feet of retail space, 1,180 parking spaces, 5 levels of parking and several payment stations.  This one is amazing, there are 6 charging stations for electric cars of the future.  Customers can pay for parking using EZ Pass, Cash, Debit Card or Credit. When a local business validates your parking ticket, you receive a special price of $4 for up to 2 hours.  There are all kinds of pricing benefits for Tanger Outlet employee&#8217;s and others.  Special monthly fee of $50 [...]]]></description>
