<p><a href="http://blog.achotelexperts.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Atlantic-City-Ballys.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-328" title="Atlantic City Bally's Casino" src="http://blog.achotelexperts.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Atlantic-City-Ballys-300x200.jpg" alt="Renovations Update for Ballys Atlantic City 2012" width="300" height="200" /></a></p>
<p><strong>Bally&#8217;s Casino in Atlantic City</strong> comprised of 3different towers, the Wild Wild West, The Claridge and Dennis Towers in addition to the main Bally&#8217;s Tower.  Previously, there slot machines and gaming tables at 3 of 4 locations.  The Claridge Tower hotel rooms will remain open but the casino gaming experience will be moved to the main area at Ballys.   The Wild West gaming area will continue to offer table games and slots as well as the Virginia City Buffet and the Mountain Bar.  The Dennis Tower and Claridge Tower will receive room upgrades and facility upgrades during the 2012 Renovation.  Look for some unique uses of the additional space created at the Claridge during the process.  Caesars Entertainment has said that it will add non gaming attractions to support the recent trend in making Atlantic City a well rounded resort destination!</p>
<p><span>One other important note, as apart of the Bally&#8217;s Renovation, new slot machines are being intalled that allow patrons to order cocktails on the screen of their favorite slot machine.  You can place a custom order and the Cocktail Server will bring your requested drink directly to you.  This is a big upgrade in service and may very well set the trend in Atlantic City!</span></p>
<p>Discount rooms at Bally&#8217;s Atlantic City can be found by calling<strong> 1-888-392-8288 </strong>or online at <strong>ACHotelExperts.com</strong></p>
