<h2>Florence and the Machine Atlantic City</h2>
<p><strong>Venue: </strong>Borgata Casino, Events Center, GA all.</p>
<p><strong>Event Date &amp; Time:</strong> 8:00 PM on Saturday May 12, 2012.</p>
<p>Tickets: <strong>Show is Sold Out but Call the AC Ticket Guys at<span style="color: #ff0000;"> 1-866-881-5373</span>, they still have tickets available. or <a title="Florence and the Machine Atlantic City" href="http://www.acticketguys.com/ResultsTicket.aspx?evtid=1819165&amp;event=Florence+And+The+Machine">Find online tickets here</a></strong></p>
<p>This is sure to be one of the best shows of 2012 at the Borgata and in Atlantic City,  as demonstrated by the show for Saturday May 12, 2012 being sold out in record time.  The Events Center will be standing only GA &#8211; General Admission with bars flanking each side of the Venue.</p>
