<div id="attachment_173" class="wp-caption alignleft" style="width: 310px"><img class="size-medium wp-image-173      " title="Game On Sports Bar Atlantic-City" src="http://blog.achotelexperts.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/Game-On-Atlantic-City-300x225.jpg" alt="Super Bowl Party 2012" width="300" height="225" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Game On #1 Place to be to watch the Super Bowl in Atlantic City!</p></div>
<p><strong>Top 10 Places to Watch Super Bowl in Atlantic City, NJ!</strong></p>
<p>If you don&#8217;t have the time or money to attend the <a title="Super Bowl Tickets" href="http://www.superbowltickets.net">2013 Super Bowl</a> in New Orleans, LA, why not go on a<br />
road trip to Atlantic City?  There are a variety of great places to watch the Super Bowl, from Irish Pubs and Sports Bars to Casino Ballrooms and exclusive party&#8217;s.  Check out our list of the Top 10  Places to Watch the Super Bowl in Atlantic City on February 3, 2013.</p>
<p><strong>1. Harry&#8217;s Oyster Bar </strong>(1st floor at Bally&#8217;s) &#8211; Free valet parking on casino side, great food, large bar over 50 LCD Tv&#8217;s and much more. Beautiful bartenders, family owned business.  Outdoor bar with TV for smokers!  Hands down the newest and best place to watch the game in AC.</p>
<p><strong>2. Hooters</strong> (Tropicana Casino) &#8211; what&#8217;s better than great wings, beautiful servers and ice cold beverages for the Super Bowl?  Exactly, choose from either location in Atlantic City.</p>
<p><strong>3. Adam Good Sports Bar</strong> (2nd floor, Tropicana Quarter) &#8211; fun sports bar known for it&#8217;s Fred Flintstone size 40 OZ beers, great food and several TV&#8217;s, great party atmosphere for 2011 Super Bowl.</p>
<p><strong>4. Mountain Bar </strong>(First Floor at Bally&#8217;s Boardwalk Side) -over 25 TV&#8217;s, large bar, great food and hot bartenders.  Just inside the Bally&#8217;s Wild West Boardwalk etrance, highly recommended for the Super Bowl.</p>
<p><strong>5. Tun Tavern</strong> (Walk AC Outlets, <a href="http://www.achotelexperts.com/hotels/sheraton_atlantic_city.html" class="kblinker" title="More about Sheraton &raquo;">Sheraton</a> AC, Convention Center) &#8211; plenty of free parking and  easy to get to.  The Tun Tavern will be rocking for Super Bowl, beautiful bartenders, great TV&#8217;s,  great food, several varieties of in house micro brews and much more.</p>
<p><strong>6. RiRa Irish Pub</strong> (2nd floor, Tropicana Quarter) &#8211; Typical Irish Pub style bar and restaurant, real Irish  bartenders, quality TV&#8217;s, large beer selection, good food, be ready to party on Super Bowl Sunday  Feb 5,  2012.</p>
<p><strong>7. Private Casino Party</strong> &#8211; look for invitations to the private casino party&#8217;s.  Generally held in the  ballroom and feature free food, celebrity guests, open bar, TV&#8217;s strategically placed around  ballroom.  Generally a free gift or gift bag is also included.  This is the VIP way to a great Super Bowl  Experience in Atlantic City, NJ.  Ask casino concierge for details.</p>
<p><strong>8. Ducktown Tavern</strong> (Georgia ave &amp; Atlantic ave near Boardwalk Hall) &#8211; #1 local bar in Atlantic  City, several high quality TV&#8217;s, great bar maids, excellent food and much more.  Generally offers beer  specials, buffet food spread, contests etc.  Really fun place to be in Atlantic City, walking distance to  Bare Exposure after the game.</p>
<p><strong>9. 40 / 40 Club</strong> (Walk AC Outlets near Caesars) &#8211; normally pretty expensive but offers plenty of  unique rooms to watch <strong>Super Bowl XLV</strong> on February 6, 2011.  Giant screen projector TV with  bleachers as well as plenty of TV&#8217;s throughout.</p>
<p><strong>10. Atlantic City Casino Bars</strong> &#8211; B Bar at Borgata, Ego Bar &amp; Lounge at Taj Mahal, Jezabel or Liquid at Trump  Plaza, Rumba Lounge at Tropicana, Spirit Bar at Showboat, Toga Bar at Caesars, Xhibition Bar at Harrah&#8217;s, 24 Hour Bar at Resorts, Dizzy Dolphin at Hilton, Firewaters at the Tropicana.</p>
<p>This list should provide you with enough great information to have an incredible time watching the  <em>Super Bowl in Atlantic City</em>, have fun and enjoy your Atlantic City Super Bowl Experience! You can find <a title="Tickets Super Bowl For Sale" href="http://www.superbowltickets.net">Super Bowl Tickets</a> For Sale here.</p>
