<h2>Revel Casino Atlantic City</h2>
<p>500 Boardwalk<br />
Revel Beach<br />
Atlantic City,<br />
New Jersey 08401</p>
<p>The latest report on the progress of the Revel Casino in Atlantic City brought to you by the AC Hotel Experts, on the ground in AC. This hotel casino will be one of the most amazing travel destinations in the USA and maybe the world.</p>
<blockquote><p><strong>UPDATE</strong> &#8211; <strong>March 20, 2012</strong>.  The soft opening will begin on April 2, 2012 and the Grand Opening will be Memorial Day weekend May 25, 26, 27, 2012.  <a title="Beyonce Concert Atlantic City at Revel Casino" href="http://events-calendar.achotelexperts.com/event/491/beyonce-atlantic-city-concert/index.html">Beyonce</a> will headline the weekend entertainment for the Grand Opening!  Rooms can be booked on the Revel Resorts website directly.</p></blockquote>
<p><strong>September 29, 2011 &#8211; Atlantic City &#8211; NJ  </strong>It&#8217;s been a long and winding road for Kevin DeSanctis, Revel&#8217;s chief executive officer who has been with the project from day one.  In fact, Kevin stayed with the project and resurrected it with the help of Governor Chris Christie.</p>
<p>Now on schedule to open in the Summer of 2012, <a title="Revel Casino" href="http://www.achotelexperts.com/casinos/revel-casino.html">Revel Casino Atlantic City </a>is at the forefront of the casino and hospitality industry.  Anyone who has been lucky enough to tour the property walks away saying, this may be one of the most advanced, incredible hotels in the world.</p>
<p>Revel was designed around it&#8217;s location on the Atlantic ocean and World Famous Boardwalk, incredible views from the minute you arrive are guaranteed.  Revel Beach will become the place to be and be seen in the summer and the property itself will wow everyone that enters it&#8217;s doors.</p>
<p>Upper level management has been hired, construction is continuing at a rapid pace, internal systems are being installed and tested, everything is moving along as planned for a summer 2012 opening.</p>
<p>Recently new sand has been pumped on to Atlantic City&#8217;s beaches and the 1,700 feet of beach in front of the Revel Casino is looking good.  It has been mentioned that there&#8217;s a possibility of a May or June 2012 <a title="Revel Atlantic City casino" href="http://www.cheapatlanticcity.com/atlantic-city-casinos/revel-casino">Revel Casino </a>Atlantic City Opening, this would mean they are ahead of schedule which is great news for Atlantic City.</p>
<h3>Atlantic City Presents Revel Casino in 2012</h3>
<p>See you at the New Revel Casino on the beach in Atlantic City, New Jersey in June &#8220;Revel Beach&#8221; will be the Gold Standard in beaches.</p>
