<h2>Guide to Atlantic City Airport Hotels</h2>
<div class="mceTemp">The Atlantic City, NJ International Airport is growing and getting in and out will become increasingly more strategic over the next 5 years.  The good news is that there are 25 hotels within 10 miles of ACY &#8211; Atlantic City Airport.</div>
<div class="mceTemp">Geographically speaking there are three locations that provide easy access to the Airport, The Black Horse Pike or Route 40, The White Horse Pike or Route 30 and inside Atlantic City to include casinos and hotels.</div>
<div class="mceTemp">You can call the <strong>Atlantic City Hotel Experts Toll Free at 1-888-392-8288 </strong>and they will help you find the perfect Airport hotel.  USE DISCOUNT CODE &#8220;AIRPORT10&#8243; for an instant discount on your next hotel reservation.</div>
<h3 class="mceTemp">Atlantic City Airport Hotels on or near the Black Horse Pike</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<div class="mceTemp"><strong>Residence By Marriott </strong>- Egg Harbor Township located on Fire RD just of the BHP and about 5 miles from the Airport.  This is an expensive option but the quality, service and amenities are top notch.</div>
</li>
<li>
<div class="mceTemp"><strong>Econo Lodge Airport </strong>- On the Black Horse Pike 5 miles from Airport.  Outdoor pool, jacuzzi tub in every room, free Wi-Fi, free deluxe breakfast daily, refrigerator in room, close to restaurants  etc</div>
</li>
<li>
<div class="mceTemp"><strong>Holiday Inn Express </strong>- on Black Horse Pike just over 5 miles for ACY.  Offers complimentary continental &#8220;Express Start&#8221; breakfast, close to restaurants and bars, free Wi-Fi, Outdoor pool and more.</div>
</li>
<li>
<div class="mceTemp"><strong>Clarion Atlantic City West </strong>- on Black Horse Pike 5 miles from Atlantic City International Airport.  Full service hotel with it&#8217;s own restaurant and bar, fitness center, free Wi-Fi, atrium lobby with over 200 rooms.</div>
</li>
<li>
<div class="mceTemp"><strong>Best Western Extended Stay</strong> &#8211; all suite hotel not far from the two listed above.  Indoor pool, excellent FREE am breakfast, daily newspaper, indoor pool and hot tub.  Highly recommended option for the value!</div>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="mceTemp">ACY Airport Hotels on the White Horse Pike</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<div class="mceTemp"><strong>Comfort Inn &amp; Suites</strong> &#8211; located on the White Horse Pike in Galloway, New Jersey is just about 5 miles from the Airport.  Indoor Pool, continental breakfast daily, free Wi-Fi, short drive to ACY. </div>
</li>
<li>
<div class="mceTemp"><strong>Country Hearth Inn &amp; Suites</strong> &#8211; White Horse Pike in Galloway, NJ.  Casino and Airport Shuttle, LCD TV&#8217;s, Free Wi-Fi and more.</div>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="mceTemp">Atlantic City Hotels and Casinos in town 9 miles from Airport</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<div class="mceTemp">The important factor here is that the Atlantic City Expressway provides all hotels in <em>Atlantic City, New Jersey </em>with a direct route to the Airport.  You can literally drive there in 15 minutes.  What does this mean?  Well, you can stay on of the 12 casinos or 30 additional hotels and still get to the <strong>Atlantic City Airport </strong>quickly and efficiently.  Now you can plan a fun night in AC and fly out the next morning no problem.  For questions about <a title="Airport Hotels Atlantic City New Jersey" href="http://www.achotelexperts.com/articles/atlantic-city-airport-hotels-acy.html">Atlantic City Airport Hotels </a>and all other lodging options in Atlantic City call 1-888-392-8288. </div>
</li>
</ul>
