<h3 class="mceTemp">
<dl id="attachment_282" class="wp-caption alignleft" style="width: 310px;">
<dt class="wp-caption-dt"><img class="size-medium wp-image-282" title="Hampton Luxury Liner" src="http://blog.achotelexperts.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/hampton-luxury-inside-400-300x200.jpg" alt="New York City to Atlantic City Bus" width="300" height="200" /></dt>
<dd class="wp-caption-dd">Free WiFi, Comfort Tech Reclining Seats, Snacks, Media Stand and more!</dd>
</dl>
</h3>
<h3>Featured Bus Transportation Company: Hampton Luxury Liner </h3>
<p>Travel to Atlantic City, New Jersey by bus from New York City / Manhattan and save money while riding in comfort.  Hampton Luxury liner offers two pick up locations in NYC and makes the trip to Atlantic City, NJ in just over 2 and half hours.  Very affordable roundtrip fee that include a casino bonus worth $45 so the trip is actually $0.</p>
<h3>New York City to Atlantic City Departures</h3>
<ul>
<li>10:15am at 33rd &amp; 7th Ave, New York City, NY</li>
<li>10:25am at 45th &amp; Broadway, New York City, NY</li>
</ul>
<h3>Per Passenger Cost &#8211; Purchase Tickets</h3>
<p><a title="Bus to Atlantic City from NYC" href="http://www.achotelexperts.com/articles/hampton-atlantic-city-luxury-liner.html">Hampton Luxury Liner Tickets to Atlantic City</a></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>$45 Roundtrip </strong>for the 6 hour day trip.  Includes a <strong>$45 Casino Bonus Package</strong> at Resorts Casino. $30 in Slot Cash, $10 Food Credit and $5 deferred coin voucher.</li>
<li><strong>$60 Roundtrip </strong>for the overnight program. Includes a <strong>$45 Casino Bonus Package </strong>at Resorts Casino. $30 in Slot Cash, $10 Food Credit and $5 deferred coin voucher.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Bus Arrival in Atlantic City, New Jersey</h3>
<ul>
<li>Hampton Luxury Liner will arrive at Resorts Casino at about 12:30pm</li>
<li>Customers can redeem Casino Bonus Package as instructed</li>
<li>The details will provided for Departure time from Atlantic City to NYC</li>
</ul>
<h3>Luxury Bus Amenities</h3>
<ul>
<li>Free WiFi Internet with section electrical outlet.</li>
<li>Free Snacks like water, chips, pretzels etc</li>
<li>News Library with magazines, news papers and brochures</li>
<li>Super comfortable reclining chairs with head rest</li>
<li>Overhead carry on storage and plenty of storage below</li>
<li>TV and Movie capabilities on the bus</li>
</ul>
<p><center><iframe width="450" height="256" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/0CTS3rx_sos" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></center></p>
<p>We get the question all the time, how do I get from New York City to Atlantic City by bus?  We found a great answer that in reality is a free trip if you include your Resorts Casino bonus.  See you in AC soon!</p>
