<p>For the first time ever, Britney Spears and Nicki Minaj will take the stage inside historic <strong>Boardwalk Hall in Atlantic City, NJ</strong>.  This amazing show will take place on Saturday August 6, 2011 beginning at 7pm.  The Femme Fatale stage show for <strong>Britney Spears in Atlantic City </strong>will be incredible, the creators of the stage show say it&#8217;s one of the best they&#8217;ve ever created.  Includes pyrotechnics, thousands of lights, video, high quality sound and a few surprises, stage hand, Elron Vegas says &#8220;if this show doesn&#8217;t blow your mind, nothing will&#8221;!</p>
<p>It is expected that Britney Spears will perform many of her new songs from the Femme Fatale Album in addition to her fan favorite former hit songs.  Nicki Minaj will perform her newest songs in addition to a few duets with Britney which should be really cool.  Here are the all the details about their upcoming concert at the Jersey Shore.</p>
<p><strong>Britney Spears with Nicki Minaj Femme Fatale Tour</strong></p>
<p>2301 Boardwalk Hall, Atlantic City, NJ 08401</p>
<p><strong>Showtime:</strong> 7:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Tickets: 1-866-881-5373</strong>  <a title="Britney Spears and Nicki Minaj Atlantic City" href="http://www.acticketguys.com/ResultsTicket.aspx?evtid=1638797&amp;event=Britney+Spears+%26+Nicki+Minaj">Britney Spears Atlantic City</a></p>
