<div id="attachment_197" class="wp-caption alignleft" style="width: 310px"><img class="size-medium wp-image-197" title="Dave Matthews Band Caravan" src="http://blog.achotelexperts.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/dave-matthews-caravan-300x206.jpg" alt="DMB Atlantic City" width="300" height="206" /><p class="wp-caption-text">June 24, 25, 26, 2011 Bader Field</p></div>
<h2>Dave Matthews Band Caravan Atlantic City</h2>
<p>DMB FAN FAVORITE SONGS: Crash Into Me, #41, Crush, Two Step, Lie In Our Graves, Ants Marching, The Best of What&#8217;s Around, If I Had It All, Don&#8217;t Drink the Water, Dancing Nancies, Dreamgirl, Cry Freedom, Smooth Rider to name a few.  Most fans are familiar with over 50 Dave Matthews Band songs.</p>
<h3>Dave Matthews Band Summer Caravan Atlantic City NJ</h3>
<p><strong>Location: </strong>Bader Field in Atlantic City, NJ</p>
<p><strong>When: </strong>June 24, 25, 26, 2011</p>
<p><strong>Tickets </strong>- Follow the dates for On Sales,  Local Ticket Source AC Ticket Guys <strong>1-866-881-5373</strong>.</p>
<h3>DMB Summer Caravan Participating Bands:</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>David Gray</strong> &#8211; You may recall the hit song &#8220;Babylon&#8221;.</li>
<li><strong>Ray LaMontagne</strong> &#8211; Born in New Jersey, known for his hit song &#8220;Trouble&#8221;.</li>
<li><strong>The Flaming Lips</strong> &#8211; Psychedelic Rock Band that remade Dark Side of the Moon.</li>
<li><strong>O.A.R</strong> &#8211; Of a Revolution, Alt Rock band with a large following from college students.</li>
<li><strong>Damian Marley </strong>- Son of Bob Marley, dance style reggae artist with 3 Grammy Awards.</li>
<li><strong>Bassnectar</strong> &#8211; Free Style Electronic Music Artist and DJ with amazing sounds and lights.</li>
<li><strong>Dr. Dog</strong> &#8211; Local Philadelphia, PA based psychedelic rock band.</li>
<li><strong>Amos Lee</strong> &#8211; Another artist from Philadelphia, folk fusion with jazz and soul.</li>
<li><strong>Thievery Corporation</strong>- Very cool band that dabbles in the ska, Dub, Indie, bossa nova genre&#8217;.</li>
</ul>
<h3>More Atlantic City Caravan Bands:</h3>
<p>Michael Franti and Spearhead, Warren Haynes Band, Grace Potter and the Nocturnals, Guster, Lotus, Rebelution, Fitz and the Tantrums, Carolina Chocolate Drops, Lisa Hannigan, Punch Brothers, From Good Homes, Delta Spirit, Big Gigantic, Alberta Cross, Mariachi El Bronx, TR3, Vusi Mahlasela, the Budos Band and Bobby Long, and exclusive performances by DMB members Carter Beauford and Stefan Lessard, and a special treat, a Dave Matthews &amp; Tim Reynolds acoustic set. </p>
<p><strong>Long Distance Shuttles</strong> &#8211; available from Philadelphia, PA, Cherry Hill, NJ, Freehold, NJ and Wilmington, DE to Atlantic City, NJ. Advance tickets required.</p>
<p><strong>Other Transportation</strong>- Car Pooling &#8211; Zimride, Bus Companies &#8211; NJ Transit, Academy, Greyhound, Trains &#8211; ACE&#8217;s from NYC, NJ Transit Rail from PHL, NY and Many other stops, Air &#8211; Atlantic City International Airport &#8211; Spirit, Air Tran &amp; More.</p>
<p><strong>Parking</strong> &#8211; keep an eye out in the Press an other local news sources for the official parking locations.  Shuttles and buses will be available on an ongoing basis from all Official Parking locations.  This process will be similar to other large sporting events like the US Open, PGA Championship, Super Bowl etc.</p>
<p><strong>VIP Experience </strong>- the former Surf Baseball Stadium previously known as Sand Castle Stadium and Bernie Robins Stadium will host a VIP experience with giant screens, elaborate food and beverage areas and much much more.</p>
<p><strong>Hotels</strong> &#8211; discounts are available at over 25 area <a title="Atlantic City New Jersey Hotels" href="http://www.achotelexperts.com">Atlantic City NJ Hotels</a>, <strong>Call 1-888-392-8288</strong> and Ask for the DMB Caravan Hotel Discount of 10%.  Ramada West Atlantic City, Lakes Bay Resort, Comfort Inn Atlantic City West and many more.</p>
